Facilitating the widest range of career assessment opportunities at the doorsteps,18th SAPE Education fair 2022 would reach out to the students of West Bengal on 18th & 19th June, 2022, organized by  SAPE Events & Media Pvt. Ltd. In which is bringing a delegation of around 50 Universities from all over India for conducting an Education Fair  at City Centre,Siliguri.The focus of the event will be to "invite students to study in under various career & courses". Apart from bringing students and best of educational institutions under one roof, the event also helps the aspirants and the guardians have a detailed discussions about the facilities and fee structures of  institutions along with expert guidance. It also facilitates an easy comparison to help in making informed decisions, best suited as per individual needs. 
India's leading colleges of different field is coming to meet students in Siliguri.The students can also gain information on education expenses that are a definite requirement to fund today’s growing expense in education. The students can also use this platform to avail scholarships and on the spot admissions. 
 
DON'T MISS TO VISIT THE FAIR 
18th & 19th JUNE 2022 
City Centre,Siliguri
Time 10am to 7pm 
ENTRY FREE🤗
